rComments: Ward's a good guy.  My one suggestion is to take a picture of the midterm questions with a cell phone camera when you get it back- he wont let you see it again, and the questions may reappear on the final.  Midterm and Final are all Essay, but no other assignments.
nice man.  take really good notes during class or else you're screwed for the midterm and final...which make up your entire grade.  no homework or projects.  exams were fair.
Knows his stuff...but tests are all essay and final is 65% of the grade, ouch
